    <item>
      <title>格鲁吉亚选举结果分歧严重，欧洲未来岌岌可危</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/georgia-votes-in-divisive-election-with-european-future-at-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚于周六举行议会选举，执政党与反对派展开竞争，反对派认为，格鲁吉亚政府与俄罗斯的关系越来越密切，危及该国加入欧盟和北约的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/georgia-votes-in-divisive-election-with-european-future-at-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国家监管机构警告称，中国正在扫描加拿大的网络防御系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-is-scanning-canada-s-cyber-defenses-state-watchdog-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大政府周五警告称，“一个来自中华人民共和国、受国家支持的复杂威胁行为者”一直在扫描重要公共实体的网络防御。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-is-scanning-canada-s-cyber-defenses-state-watchdog-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 22:29:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>密西西比州邮寄选票逾期被共和党裁定为非法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/late-mail-ballots-in-mississippi-ruled-illegal-in-gop-challenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦上诉法院裁定，密西西比州在选举日后接受邮寄选票的行为违反了美国法律，但将其裁决是否适用于 11 月 5 日总统大选的问题发回给了下级法院的法官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/late-mail-ballots-in-mississippi-ruled-illegal-in-gop-challenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 22:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>G7 敲定 500 亿美元乌克兰贷款，由俄罗斯资产担保</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/g-7-finalizes-50-billion-ukraine-loan-backed-by-russian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七国集团最终确定向乌克兰提供 500 亿美元贷款，贷款由俄罗斯央行冻结资产产生的利润支持，为急需的援助尽快流入基辅铺平了道路，并在很大程度上保护了关键融资不受美国总统大选结果的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/g-7-finalizes-50-billion-ukraine-loan-backed-by-russian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 21:53:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行行长拒绝将食品从通胀目标中剔除</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/rbi-chief-pushes-back-on-calls-to-cut-food-from-inflation-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行行长沙克提坎塔·达斯拒绝了一位高级政府顾问提出的将波动较大的食品价格从通胀目标中剔除的提议，称此举对普通消费者来说毫无意义。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/rbi-chief-pushes-back-on-calls-to-cut-food-from-inflation-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 21:43:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国和约旦警告以色列在加沙犯下战争罪行和种族清洗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/un-jordan-warn-of-israeli-war-crimes-ethnic-cleansing-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国最高人权官员表示，以色列在加沙地带北部犯下的罪行可能构成反人类罪，而约旦最高外交官则称以色列在那里的行为是“种族清洗”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/un-jordan-warn-of-israeli-war-crimes-ethnic-cleansing-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 21:21:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁担心亚太经合组织峰会可能因反犯罪抗议活动而中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/peru-is-worried-apec-summit-may-be-disrupted-by-anti-crime-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁政府越来越担心最近的反犯罪抗议活动可能会延续到下个月，并扰乱亚太地区世界领导人峰会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/peru-is-worried-apec-summit-may-be-disrupted-by-anti-crime-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 21:04:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国调查与中国有关的黑客入侵电信系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/us-investigating-breach-of-telecoms-by-china-linked-hackers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府周五表示，正在调查中国政府附属黑客针对商业电信领域进行的未经授权的访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/us-investigating-breach-of-telecoms-by-china-linked-hackers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 20:30:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃里克·亚当斯寻求在纽约市长初选前于三月接受审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/nyc-mayor-blasts-leaks-as-he-seeks-dismissal-of-bribery-charge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 要求在三月份对针对他的联邦贿赂案进行审判，以便陪审团在 2025 年 6 月市长初选之前决定他的命运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/nyc-mayor-blasts-leaks-as-he-seeks-dismissal-of-bribery-charge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 17:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯与碧昂斯同行；特朗普与罗根一起前往德克萨斯州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/trump-with-rogan-beyonce-to-join-harris-in-rival-texas-trips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在距离选举日如此近的时间内，唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯将中断摇摆州竞选，转而前往一个意想不到的地点——德克萨斯州，这个州是共和党总统候选人的坚定支持者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/trump-with-rogan-beyonce-to-join-harris-in-rival-texas-trips</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 15:10:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
